venv/
streamlit_log.txt

# Note: pricing_data.db is intentionally NOT ignored here.
# On Streamlit Community Cloud the filesystem is ephemeral / resets on
# redeploy, so if you want data to persist across deploys you have two options:
#   1. Commit pricing_data.db to the repo (fine for a small internal tool,
#      but everyone will need to `git pull` to see teammates' latest edits —
#      not real-time shared).
#   2. Switch to a hosted DB (see README "Scaling to real multi-user sharing").
# For a true shared, always-up-to-date experience, option 2 is recommended.
